<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #0ea5e9; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #0ea5e9; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    .amount { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #0ea5e9; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Thank You for Your Support! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @owner.name %>,</p>

      <p>Your donation to ChurchNeeds.net has been successfully set up!</p>

      <div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280;">Your Donation Amount</p>
        <p class="amount" style="margin: 10px 0;">$<%= @subscription.amount_in_dollars %></p>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280;">Billed yearly</p>
      </div>

      <p>Your support helps us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Keep ChurchNeeds.net free for all churches</li>
        <li>Cover hosting and infrastructure costs</li>
        <li>Develop new features and improvements</li>
        <li>Provide reliable service to the church community</li>
      </ul>

      <p>You can manage your subscription, update the amount, or cancel at any time from your account settings.</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= manage_donations_url %>" class="button">Manage Subscription</a>
      </div>

      <p>Thank you for being part of our mission to serve churches!</p>

      <p>Blessings,<br>The ChurchNeeds.net Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Roaring Lamb Productions<br>
      Questions? <a href="<%= new_contact_url %>">Contact our support team</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
